    <div class="row">
      <div class="box ans col">
        <p><i class="icon fa-solid fa-arrow-right fa-1x"></i>
            Monoalphabetic cipher is substitution cipher technique where each letter in the messgae is mapped to a key letter. This technique stronger than ceaser cipher as the key space is larger and there are 26! possibilites of key generation. Still, this technique can be cracked with help of double frequency distribution.</p>
      </div>
